{"tid":1531763,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大和民族果然係優等民族","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:35:23.000Z","uid":258326,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"068887696dcb03e3068ba7af3e126e20e8520fe6","tid":1531763,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>溝出嚟啲彈都勁過人</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa63Hb4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa63Hb4.gif&h=81a3009c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原片：三里塚闘争<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eXjd7GkHKfU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR0XbMmgF7KST1aFAroRY2c0BRUIx1Iuw6TSaMWtPneJYT2L7WzhtRbxV2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeXjd7GkHKfU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR0XbMmgF7KST1aFAroRY2c0BRUIx1Iuw6TSaMWtPneJYT2L7WzhtRbxV2E&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR24aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2b25d17b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eXjd7GkHKfU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR0XbMmgF7KST1aFAroRY2c0BRUIx1Iuw6TSaMWtPneJYT2L7WzhtRbxV2E</a>"},{"pid":"0100298f4bfa253c4b4d13f82997312a1ddfb962","tid":1531763,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa992e7f4a7406d930cc55d655d4402eddd3540","tid":1531763,"uid":182822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"我地啲彈係公安溝㗎嘛<br />\n想燒死自己人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f8c0f5a83f864ba28ec3657021f3ee74ad7b8f","tid":1531763,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"(LIHKG please set up an English Platform for us) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> US Congress will be resumed on 9/9!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> Please join the march on 8/9 to voice out our desire of passing the <br />\n&quot;Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&quot;!<br />\n</span> </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531140</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARgCLoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARgCLoO.j